sandhippoma ( tamil : shall we meet ? ) is a 1998 tamil language romance film directed by indrakumar . the film features suriya and preetha vijayakumar in the lead roles , while raadhika , prakash raj , sarath babu and ambika also play significant roles . deva composed the film 's soundtrack while rathnavelu handled the camera work . the film released in july 1998 . it was dubbed into telugu as viswam .